      "writtenOn": "2021-02-11T04:52:18Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "it is true that that task will do nothing in case of build-number-based invocations, but this CL changes *generic* code that must not assume that it will be used only in that case. A future reader of the updated proto comments might think that they can create a finalizing invocation that includes finalized invocations and it will work the same way as CreateInvocation+FinalizeInvocation (except it won\u0027t).\n\nI think creation of a finalized invocation must work the same way as creation of an invocation immediately followed by finalization.",
      "parentUuid": "95dc4a8f_db1f487b",
      "revId": "477e9165a4617fb2fed6e6ecb4fe6d716532a39f",
