      "side": 1,
      "message": "Agreed (sorry for the misleading comment in https://chromium-review.googlesource.com/c/infra/infra/+/2685271).\n\nBut now I\u0027m wondering if it\u0027s worth complicating the CreateInvocation for this special case to save a RPC. Does it violates the single-responsibility principle?",
