      "writtenOn": "2021-02-11T05:50:08Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "idk if it violates SRP (the responsibility is still to create an invocation), but I definitely agree that it is more complexity. I think making two sequential RPCs during build creation would increase build creation latency, so I\u0027d like to avoid that. I\u0027d be OK with either a proper implementation of this CL, or creating finalization task on bb side.",
